{
  "stem": "490.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I used to sit with those people, a lot of youngsters sitting down and give them a little pep-- pep talk.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And just looking to the future, that some day-- it was not meant that this should be the end.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were able to once in a while to even to, to have a concert.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there were some people musicians, some good musicians, which they managed to hold back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they organized-- we organized between ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had once in a while some music playing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then if you were young, you sort of hold onto life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after you came back from the, from work, you were able still to sit down.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes, you would play cards or sometimes, you know, to go to a-- listen to music or to go to even to say a prayer.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, well, I'm not talking now about concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those are the labor camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These labor camps were geared to protect the work-- the people, because they needed our service.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there's one-- to tell you the conditions the way they was, there is one-- we used to come-- in the morning, they used to get out of the camps, the barracks, and stand up, stay in line, to be counted.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then you marched off to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Coming back, it was the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had to stand in line to be counted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one day, we came back from work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they lined us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] And then they called a name, which it was right in my barrack, only two seats away from the bunker that I slept.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they ask him, who sleeps in this and this place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were young fellow walked out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
